Orascom Construction Board Approves $1.1 Dividend Per Share

-- B y   A h m e d   A   N a m a t a l l a
-- 
2011-09-15T08:49:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/orascom-construction-board-approves-1-1-dividend-per-share.html
Orascom Construction Industries,
 Egypt ’s biggest publicly traded builder, said its board of
directors approved distributing a $1.1 per share dividend, or a
total of $229.8 million.  The payment is the first instalment of the company’s
dividend distribution plan of up to 3 billion Egyptian pounds
($504 million), it said in a filing to the Egyptian bourse
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ahmed A Namatalla in Cairo at 
 anamatalla@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mahmoud Kassem at 
 mkassem1@bloomberg.net  